include includes/head
body
  include includes/nav
  .container
    header.hero-unit
      h1 Committee Roles
      p Roles and Responsibilities for members of the organizing committee
      
    section#chair
      .page-header
        h2 Chair
      ul
        li Put together the Organizing Committee
        li Coordinate with event/organization that VizSec is co-locate with 
        li Coordinate with co-located event to get complimentary registration for keynote, other guests
        li Set up budget
        li Publicize on mailing lists, online calendars, blogs, social media
        li Bring in sponsors
        li Find a keynote speaker

    section#programchair
      .page-header
        h2 Program Chair
      ul
        li Put together the Program Committee
        li Write Call for Papers
        li Set up reviewing site (<a href='http://www.easychair.org/'>easychair</a>)
        li Assign reviewers (at least 3 per paper)
        li Determine the accepted papers based on reviews (no more than 12 papers)
        li Notify authors of acceptance/rejection
        li Determine program schedule
        li Chair the program onsite, including keeping to a schedule (have time remaining signs)

    section#publicationchair
      .page-header
        h2 Publication Chair
      ul
        li Set up agreement with ACM for proceedings in the <a href='https://www.acm.org/publications/icp_series'>International Conference Proceedings Series</a>, including free access for two weeks prior
        li Get ISBN number
        li Get copyrights from authors for all accepted papers
        li Provide copyright block for papers to authors
        li Collect camera ready papers from authors
        li Check formatting of papers, fix minor issues, communicate to authors
        li Generate frontmatter for proceedings <a href='https://www.acm.org/publications/icps-instructions/'>(instructions)</a>
        li Send papers on to ACM
        li Send papers to whoever puts them onto a USB drive for the conference
        li Ensure that papers are available two weeks before the event and mail the URL to the vizsec mailing list

    section#webmaster
      .page-header
        h2 Webmaster
      ul
        li Update site with organizing and program committee
        li Update site with CFP
        li Update site with program schedule
      
    include includes/foot